  <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$b" id="aspace_79c8695a9898803649957bcce09f6282">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>The papers contain notes, drafts and clippings. The material demonstrates Hearon's working methods--background research, sketched out ideas, revisions. The clippings contain book reviews, interviews and some biographical information.</p>  </scopecontent>
